{"tid":1685033,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全盛時期嘅律政司，可以向市民申請幾多禁制令？","createTime":"2019-10-31T11:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T08:03:09.000Z","uid":186,"like":441,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"0ecbc9d3356daa3d2447cdb0576eb4c3def5d20d","tid":1685033,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"而法庭又批<br />\n<br />\n相反，市民申請臨時禁制令。又唔見佢批"},{"pid":"77dab327edd53ac08cf035451544edf8111fea8e","tid":1685033,"uid":186,"like":26,"dislike":14,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:04:14.000Z","msg":"律政司司長以公眾利益守護者身份，今天入稟高等法院申請禁制令，禁止任何人非法於網上論壇及通訊軟件，包括連登及 telegram，發佈任何訊息或言論可促進、鼓勵或煽動其他人士威脅使用暴力，包括非法傷害他人及損壞香港的任何財物，或協助及教唆他人作出相關行為。高等法院今緊急開庭處理，並頒下臨時禁制令，時效至下月 15 日。"},{"pid":"27b76123164253a9b0201a785062e98ecb968e31","tid":1685033,"uid":191926,"like":142,"dislike":0,"score":142,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:04:26.000Z","msg":"三權合作已成事實"},{"pid":"f9e0fc70ff91ad9752a170e1609be0ffaed0567f","tid":1685033,"uid":252064,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEHiYQ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEHiYQ7.jpg&h=9b7c4b87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f861c3f617c9d7f6017ac7c643768247c9e726d2","tid":1685033,"uid":73565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0ecbc9d3356daa3d2447cdb0576eb4c3def5d20d","tid":1685033,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"而法庭又批<br />\n<br />\n相反，市民申請臨時禁制令。又唔見佢批"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:04:39.000Z","msg":"市民好少"},{"pid":"8c04f6dedb93a15958cdd6ebdc60f0c11697b293","tid":1685033,"uid":186,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"機場臨時禁制令<br />\n起低禁制令<br />\n咩都禁制"},{"pid":"075395513987849f2b8ed1eb1f75fd8170320883","tid":1685033,"uid":186,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"f861c3f617c9d7f6017ac7c643768247c9e726d2","tid"